{"word":"ἀμβλυώσσω","slug":"ἀμβλυώσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀμβλυώσσω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀμβλύς'><el>ἀμβλύς</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a>\n<p/><i>to be dim-sighted</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ἀμβλ. πρὸς τὸ φῶς</el> <i>to be blind</i> to it, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/>"}]}